Version 0.4.5 (Nausicaa) - 2006/12/10
 + Multi-currencies support in portfolio and matrix
 + Quotes Management (List Downloading, Editing, ...)
 + Yahoo connector fully functionnal for NASDAQ/AMEX/NYSE markets
 + Euronext connector for EURONEXT/ALTERNEXT/ML markets
 + more MMI enhancements
 + Import / Export historic data
 + binary installation package for Windows
 + RSI and Stochastic indicators

Version 0.4.2 (Coca2) - Patch 1 - 2006/10/03
 + Bug fixing
 + realtime connector for live data is live again

Version 0.4.2 (Coca2) - 2006/05/28
 + MMI enhancements
 + realtime connector for live data differed 15 min.

Version 0.4 (Coca) - DONE - 2006/03/11
 + generic live/import quotes data plugins
 + realtime connector for live data (euronext market only)
 + portfolio management (create, delete, rename, select)
 + better autorefresh the trading matrix (thread)
 + realtime front panel with notebook and last trades
 + alerts back-end
 + Deferred settlement service (SRD) basic

Version 0.3 (Popotka - The Toy Software) - DONE - 2005/11/27
